episodes.overview: Dora and her friends explore Troll Land, a secret place where the Grumpy Old Troll lives. In this kind of dimension, everything rhymes.

episodes.name: Pepe's School Day Adventure
episodes.overview: Dora tries to help Pepe the Pig win a popcorn party at school.

episodes.name: Dora's Enchanted Forest Adventures, Part 1: Tale of the Unicorn King
episodes.overview: Unicornio has been chosen to be king of the forest, so Dora and Boots help him get to his castle.

episodes.name: Halloween Parade
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots must help Little Monster find a costume so he can march in the Halloween parade.

episodes.name: Dora's Enchanted Forest Adventures, Part 2: The Secret of Atlantis
episodes.overview: Dora, Boots, Diego, and King Unicornio leave the Enchanted Forest to end an ancient feud between the unicorns and the dragons, and to save the lost continent of Atlantis. Meanwhile, a greedy owl is given the opportunity to act as king and watch over the forest.

episodes.name: Dora's Enchanted Forest Adventures, Part 3: Dora Saves King Unicornio
episodes.overview: The Enchanted Forest is in grave peril as the owl usurped Unicornio's position as king and trapped Unicornio. Dora and Boots must venture into the forest to rescue Unicornio and teach the owl a lesson.

episodes.name: The Big Red Chicken‚Äôs Magic Wand
episodes.overview: The Big Red Chicken is doing magic tricks and for his first trick, he turns Boots into a chicken. When he tries to turn him back into a monkey, he lets out a big sneeze that propels the magic wand into Magic Land. Dora and friends set off on a magic-filled journey in order to get the wand fixed so Boots can become a monkey again.

episodes.name: Swiper's Favorite Things
episodes.overview: Swiper is packing all of his favorite things for a sleepover at his Grandma‚Äôs House ‚Äî his pajama trunk, his favorite puppy book, and his very special funny bunny. Just as he is about to leave, a big wind gust comes in and blows everything away! Dora and Swiper journey to Crocodile Lake, through the Jumbled Trees, and race to Strawberry Hill to get Swiper‚Äôs favorite things back

episodes.name: A Ribbon for Pinto
episodes.overview: Dora, Boots and Pinto are heading to the big horse show, but the train breaks down on the way.

episodes.name: Dora's Knighthood Adventure
episodes.overview: Boots loves to hear stories about knights who go on heroic adventures and Don Quixote (Andy Garcia) tells Dora and Boots that anyone can be a knight as long as they help others. Boots would love to be a knight and so would his friends Rocinante the horse and Dapple the donkey, but they need someone to rescue. Dora takes out her spotting scope and they discover a princess calling out for help from the Royal Garden. Dora, Boots, Rocinante and Dapple set out through the Puppet Stage, past Tico‚Äôs Carousel to get to the Royal Garden and save the princess.

episodes.name: Dora's Easter Adventure
episodes.overview: Swiper‚Äôs up to no good again and Dora, Boots and their new friend the Hip-Hop Bunny must stop him.

episodes.name: Feliz Dia de los Padres (Father's Day)
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots are in trouble! They're stuck in the quicksand! The Super Babies are on their way to rescue them! They need to go over the Troll Bridge, through the Spooky Forest, and over to the quicksand so that they can pull Dora and Boots out!

episodes.name: Dora's Rescue in Mermaid Kingdom
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots turn into sea creatures to help a lost mermaid return to her mother.

episodes.name: Dora's Fantastic Gymnastics Adventure
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots are practicing for the Fantastic Gymnastics Show when Dora gets a special delivery: a beautiful rainbow ribbon. But Swiper came and swiped the ribbon so the duo must get it back in time for the show.

episodes.name: School Science Fair
episodes.overview: Dora and Emma are bringing a project volcano to the Green Power Science Fair with new friends.

episodes.name: Dora's Moonlight Adventure
episodes.overview: Dora takes care of some kittens for Abuela, but they go missing.

episodes.name: Perrito's Big Surprise
episodes.overview: There's a surprise waiting for Perrito, but Swiper wants to swipe the present! Will Dora be able to prevent Swiper from doing so at Surprise Hill?

episodes.name: Dora and Diego's Amazing Animal Circus
episodes.overview: Boots and Baby Jaguar are having an animal circus, and Dora and Diego rush to get there.

episodes.name: Benny the Castaway
episodes.overview: Benny gets stranded on the crazy, deserted Coconut Island, and it's up to Dora and Boots to save him.

episodes.name: Baby Bongo's Big Music Show
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots take Baby Bongo on a musical adventure as they race to the Big Music Show in time for Baby Bongo's first performance.

episodes.name: Vamos a Pintar! (Let's Paint!)
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots have to bring their special paintbrush to help their painter friend at the art studio.

episodes.name: Check Up Day
episodes.overview: Dora is at the doctor's office for her yearly check up. There, she meets a few animals who are sick and learns that getting a shot isn't as bad as it looks.

episodes.name: Little Map
episodes.overview: Map shows his nephew, Little Map, how to draw pictures and make a treasure map. Soon, Dora and Boots go on a treasure hunt of their own.

episodes.name: Dora's Thanksgiving Day Parade
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots rush to get Dora's float back for the Thanksgiving Day parade when the Pirate Piggies cause it to fly away.

episodes.name: Royal Rescue
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots become a lady knight and a squire, and assist a noble horse in saving Don Quixote, who's been captured by an evil wizard and is being held in an abandoned library.

episodes.name: Book Explorers
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots visit the library, where they jump into books, meet characters of books, and help them find their lost items.

episodes.name: The Butterfly Ball
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots must help their butterfly friend, Mariposa, attend the Butterfly Ball, where everyone gets their special set of wings.

episodes.name: Dora Rocks!
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots have to get to Benny's barn so they can use Dora's microphone to invite their friends over for a sing-along party.

episodes.name: Dora's Royal Rescue
episodes.overview: Dora, Boots and Rocinante head to Story Castle to rescue Don Quixote from an evil wizard.

episodes.name: Dora and Perrito to the Rescue
episodes.overview: Dora and her dog rush to the Big River to save Boots.

episodes.name: Puppies Galore
episodes.overview: Dora and her pals accompany a bunch of puppies to rescue a young dog named Little Boots.

episodes.name: Catch That Shape Train
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots make a train out of shapes in Boots' sticker book, and they jump in to retrieve the forgotten steering wheel before the train heads for the final turn on the tracks.

episodes.name: Kittens in Mittens
episodes.overview: Dora reads "The Three Little Kittens" to Abuela's new cat, Lucky, and jumps into the book of nursery rhymes to help the kittens find their mittens.

episodes.name: Dora's Great Roller Skate Adventure
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots put on their roller skates and take off on a skating adventure to open Skate Park for everyone.

episodes.name: Verde's Birthday Party!
episodes.overview: Dora, Boots, and Verde the Clean-Up Truck must clear up a flood at Party Park in time for Verde's birthday party.

episodes.name: Dora's and Sparky's Riding Adventure!
episodes.overview: Dora helps Sparky the Horse feel better, and then takes him for a ride before returning him to the barn.

episodes.name: Dora's Rainforest Talent Show
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots put on their roller skates and take off on a skating adventure to open Skate Park for everyone.

episodes.name: Dora and Diego in the Time of Dinosaurs
episodes.overview: Dora and Diego travel back to prehistoric times and go on a dinosaur adventure.

episodes.name: Dora's Ice Skating Spectacular
episodes.overview: Dora and Boots must help the Snow Princess defeat the Ice Witch in a skating contest in order to win back everyone's skates.

episodes.name: Riding the Roller Coaster Rocks
episodes.overview: Dora, Boots and Abuela search for the secret door to an amusement park.

episodes.name: Dora in Wonderland
episodes.overview: When Dora's kittens run through a magic mirror, Dora and Boots end up in Wonderland.

episodes.name: Dora‚Äôs Museum Sleepover Adventure
episodes.overview: Dora brings a magic cape to the prince's castle to break a spell.

episodes.name: Dora's Super Soccer Showdown
episodes.overview: Dora travels to Brazil to play in the Big Cup Soccer Tournament against a team of soccer-playing monsters.

episodes.name: Dora Saves Fairytale Land
episodes.overview:
Dora and Boots try to keep a very sleepy Baby Bear awake long enough to get her home for her winter nap.

episodes.overview: Dora, Emma and Kate help Gus the Bus take all of the instruments to the kids at Music School.
